@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #0056b3;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .policy-section {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

        .policy-section h2 {
            color: #333;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #0056b3;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .policy-section p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .policy-section ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

            .policy-section ul li {
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #888;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }
</style>

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container">
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>We are committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you visit or use our football league website.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: Name, email address, and other contact details when you create an account or subscribe to newsletters.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Information about how you use the website, such as pages visited and time spent on the site.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: Small data files stored on your device to enhance user experience and provide analytics.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>The information we collect may be used for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Improving the user experience on our website.</li>
            <li>Sending updates, newsletters, or notifications related to the football league.</li>
            <li>Analyzing site performance and user behavior to improve content.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties, except:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To comply with legal requirements.</li>
            <li>With trusted third-party service providers who help us operate the site, under strict confidentiality agreements.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>5. Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no online system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access and update your personal information.</li>
            <li>Request the deletion of your data.</li>
            <li>Opt out of any communications by unsubscribing from emails.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review it periodically.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at privacy@ligafutebol.com.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    &copy; 2024 Liga Futebol. All rights reserved.
</footer>
